Dear Bioconductor Community,

As we approach the holiday season, we have a few exciting updates and opportunities we wish to share with you:

New Bioconductor Website Launching January 3rd
Our new website design is focused on being more welcoming and accessible. Preview it at http://new.bioconductor.org and provide feedback in Slack #biocwebsite. [Note that https is not supported on the preview but will be active once live.]

Bioconductor Carpentries Instructor Recruitment
Join us as an instructor to shape the future of Bioconductor education. Apply here: https://forms.gle/HEBUcRJh814XPqe4A.

Upcoming Collaboration Session with the Carpentries
Join us on December 29th, 4-5PM PST to learn how to translate Bioconductor Carpentries lessons using Crowdin i.e. AI supported translation [DeepL + Google Translation API + ChatGPT API]. Details in the community calendar: https://carpentries.org/community/

EuroBioC2024 Sticker Contest
Design the official conference sticker and win free registration. Enter by January 31st here: https://forms.gle/ALx3UUAuqzcazGbeA.

For more details on each of these, please visit the respective links provided above.

We appreciate your ongoing contribution to the Bioconductor community and look forward to an exciting 2024.

